reviewText: Arrived on time and very good quality, I am sure all have seen these movies....If not get your family together and some popcorn and laugh your heart out.  Delightfully funny movies to enjoy with family and friends.

This is a great family series of movies! we've watched this over and over. The first one deals with career and family pressures, and the second one deals with a final summer retreat for the family, with hilarious outcomes. If you're into balancing these things and life at the cottage this is a must for your collection!
After seeing the two film. I found them to be enjoyable, though the first whilst did have it comedic moments , it also had its moment that pulled my heart with tears. The second film was too funny.
Havent watched part II yet but so far so good its been great.
CHRISTMAS GIFT WOULD ORDER AGAIN

I saw these movies many times when I was younger and preceded to watch them to death, checked them out recently (after five years of not viewing them) and fell in love with them again. Surprisingly I appreciate these films even more now, as when I was younger all I watched them for was the comedy aspect. But now, I find these just as entertaining as all the story archs between family members and life lessons displayed in these, mean a lot more to me now (having expereinced a couple of them myself).

There are a few nitpicks I have with them (check my reviews on them) but this easily gets 5/5 as these are trully well done movies that can be enjoyed by adults and children alike.

This is a family movie all the way.  It's totally hilarious and funny (I personally think that the average middle aged person today doesn't know what funny is cause they've grown up with a very "sick" type of humor).  This is clean, funny and I watch it over and over and never get tired of it.  I look forward to having my grandchildren watch it someday with me and I know they'll love it too.  It's nice that there is humor around that doesn't have to be sexual in nature (altho they try to use sexual humor with the one woman in it....you'll know who when you see her).  Unfortunately, they seem to have to "sex" it up no matter what you look at in this day and age, even commercials!
Love these movies.  My kids have watched them several times.  Great life lessons, makes you appreciate family, even with our differences.
Two very entertaining movies that kept me laughing throughout!  All the actors did a great job too!  It feels like I know this family because they seemed so real-life!

These are quintessential family movies--ones that have something for everyone to enjoy and clean/no objectionable content, IMO.
